title: Screenshots!
content:
Hi. For my website I'm gonna need lots of screenshots.
Rules

*Take screenshots from Original games or Mods
*Keep them 16 colors
*Keep them 320x200 pixels (or whatever the original size is.)
*Post them right in your post or if you have a lot, post a download.
*tell me whether or not you want to be credited for it.[img]http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v609/genius314/picturekeen.bmp[/img]
